          ],
          "workingSteps": [
            "Numerator $2x^2+5x+3$: $ac=6$, sum $5$: $2$ and $3$; $\\Rightarrow (2x+3)(x+1)$",
            "Check: $(2x+3)(x+1)=2x^2+2x+3x+3=2x^2+5x+3$ ✓",
            "Denominator $2x^2-x-3$: $ac=-6$, sum $-1$: $-3$ and $2$; $\\Rightarrow (2x-3)(x+1)$",
            "Check: $(2x-3)(x+1)=2x^2+2x-3x-3=2x^2-x-3$ ✓",
            "$\\dfrac{(2x+3)(x+1)}{(2x-3)(x+1)} = \\dfrac{2x+3}{2x-3}$"
          ]
